      <talk_answer link_index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-a" mid="38" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>I heard that there's a genius poet called <FONT color=#a82424>Bard</FONT> travelling in the <FONT color=#a82424>Blue Wind Plains</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-b" mid="39" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>Though eras may change, history remains. If we don't record down the story of the Alicantos in any way we can, their tragedy will soon vanish from peoples' memories.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1835_conscience_pope-2" mid="40" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Though I'm not certain about it, I'll do so if it's your wish.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>I could record their story down myself, but I think it would be much better if it's recreated into a masterpiece by the genius poet Bard so that more people can read it. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="55"><![CDATA[<html>$Crazy Mad Bard$<BR>Who art thou... What brings thou hither...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-2" image="QW_108.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>Then please make your way to the <FONT color=#a82424>Blue Wind Plains</FONT> and tell Genius Bard about this. Thank you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2-a" mid="42" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes, it's me.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Crazy Mad Bard$<BR>Who art thou... What brings thou hither... Oh it's you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2-b" mid="43" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I don't really understand what you mean but I'm pretty sure that's not the case.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Crazy Mad Bard$<BR>Don't tell me you've encountered the artistic soul of the universe and the passion like the howling wolves made you take the path of a vagabond?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2-c" mid="44" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Tell him about the Alicantos' tragic story.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Crazy Mad Bard$<BR>Hmm... Then why are you here?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2-d" mid="45" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Crazy Mad Bard$<BR>Ah… ah…!! <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Mad Bard shivers with a sudden surge of emotions.)</FONT><BR>This… this is…!!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2-e" mid="46" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(What is he saying??)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Crazy Mad Bard$<BR><FONT color=#a94407>Inspiriation--------!!</FONT><BR>Striking me like a lightning through the stormy clouds!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2-f" mid="47" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Can he really do a good job?)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Crazy Mad Bard$<BR>Who else but I shall record down such a magnificent and tragic history?!<BR>That's right! This is a fierce history that should be remembered forever!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-3" mid="48" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Maybe he'll do a good job.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Crazy Mad Bard$<BR>How futile goodness is... It eventually gets harassed by evil and vanishes like a mirage... But if I don't record down about the goodness in words, no one can bear the anger for the evil in their hearts...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Crazy Mad Bard$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Mad Bard seems to be thinking of what to write. Go back to Pero.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1835_conscience_pope-3-a" mid="51" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes, he agreed to write a poem.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>Have you met Bard?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1835_conscience_pope-3-b" mid="52" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>That's great news. Thank you.</html>]]></talk_question>
